tokensByWeek %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = date, y = nTrans)) +
  geom_line()

tokensByWeek %>%
  gather(key = type, value = val, -date, -blockNum) %>%
  mutate(val = as.integer(val)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = date, y = val, color = type)) + geom_line() +
  facet_wrap(facets = 'type', scales = 'free_y')
